title: [The Carpenter's Cozy]
description: Braided rugs, slightly lumpy where the cover the sand, are spread throughout the small room that is encircled by pressed canvas walls.  Wrought iron lanterns, three in total, shed light upon the tables, that they are hung over, and the nearby chairs fashioned of broken ship's wheels.  Passage into the other areas of the pavilion are cleared for easy navigation.
